{"tid":1264830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，唔好放棄呀! 絕對有機會嫁，入黎睇一睇就知點解!","createTime":"2019-06-29T01:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T06:58:26.000Z","uid":4796,"like":47,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"616befe487398aeef5aca1a251520b9198a3fe39","tid":1264830,"uid":4796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:10:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>依家焦點越黎越模糊喇! 我地目標要好清晰!</strong> <br />\n香港搞成咁，就係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨</span></strong>! <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨貪污腐敗，搜刮民脂民膏，全面監控人民，控制言論自由! </span></strong>其實好多大陸人都好討厭，但敢怒不敢言! 依家開始想全面控制香港大家有眼睇!<br />\n相信大家都好同意，單靠香港力量，好難做到d咩，所以我地今次必需要有一場真正既革命，聯合中台港澳既人，去完成呢個民主運動!<br />\n<br />\n從今日起，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地必須目標清晰，對準中共暴政!</span></span></strong><br />\n咁先可以真正得民心!!!"},{"pid":"247dae4fb34b7b65819f773d69330fce7acdf7b1","tid":1264830,"uid":4796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48998f7630737f176af8b8577afd1be60fb2998c","tid":1264830,"uid":50835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"即刻改返 抵讚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個標題睇落開心好多"},{"pid":"1e619a5428969b3c76f6143e1d37bb4ea47d9642","tid":1264830,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c151b1abaf437d4f8e36310e6cdc8c8a40a0a23","tid":1264830,"uid":4796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48998f7630737f176af8b8577afd1be60fb2998c","tid":1264830,"uid":50835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"即刻改返 抵讚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個標題睇落開心好多"},"citedBy"